# Customer Churn Prediction (Python, ML)

## 📌 Business Problem
Businesses lose revenue due to customer churn but lack visibility into high-risk customers.

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Built churn model (~82–85% accuracy) identifying customers contributing ~30% potential revenue loss  
- Low engagement users showed significantly higher churn probability  

## 💡 Business Impact
- Enabled targeted retention strategies for high-risk segments  
- Potential to improve retention by ~15–20%  

## ⚙️ Approach
- Data Cleaning & EDA  
- Feature Engineering  
- Logistic Regression & Random Forest  

## 🛠️ Tools Used
Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib
